General.Name: Fagerhult AB
General.Description: Fagerhult Group AB, together with its subsidiaries, manufactures and sells professional lighting solutions worldwide. It offers indoor and outdoor lighting products for use in offices, schools, healthcare, retail, park and city centers, road and city streets, sports halls, and urban environments under the ateljé Lyktan, iGuzzini, LED Linear, WE-EF, Fagerhult, LTS, Arlight, Eagle Lighting, Whitecroft, Designplan Lighting, i-Valo, and Veko brand names. The company was formerly known as AB Fagerhult (publ.) and changed its name to Fagerhult Group AB in 2023. Fagerhult Group AB was founded in 1945 and is headquartered in Habo, Sweden.
